Despite her latest accomplishments Whittam is not standing still, and is already thinking of fresh plans for the future when she returns to the UK after this weekend's fight, admitting she'd relish the opportunity to work with Floyd Mayweather.

She added: 'Because of the rate we're rapidly expanding the immediate plan is to hire more staff when we get back.

'I'd love to do a pair for Floyd (Mayweather), as I think we could go really flamboyant, after judging by what he's worn at his previous fights at the MGM. 

'So one day it'd be nice for Fight Label to be up there in and amongst the Mayweather fame.'

